{"tid":2495204,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［感謝中國］Amazon《魔戒》MMORPG新作取消開發，因「香港樂遊」被騰訊收購致合作生變","createTime":"2021-04-19T04:59:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T05:37:43.000Z","uid":109923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"76123903c11d769a6e4d7e4627c930ac27905672","tid":2495204,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T04:59:35.000Z","msg":"2018 年，香港樂遊科技（Leyou）於成立新遊戲工作室 Athlon Games，與 Amazon Games 合作開發 J.R.R 托爾金知名小說《魔戒》（The Lord of the Rings）世界觀的 MMORPG新作，如今因騰訊收購樂遊科技後，該開發項目被取消了。<br />\n <br />\n根據彭博社記者 Jason Schreier 採訪（Bloomberg），不願具名的內部人士披露，<span class=\"red\">樂遊科技自 2020 年 12 月被中國騰訊收購後，《魔戒》MMO 新作的開發合約內容產生 Amazon 與騰訊公司之間的糾紛</span>，最終導致遊戲取消開發，負責該項目的 Amazon 團隊將會轉往其他專案。<br />\n <br />\n之後，Amazon 發言人向彭博社證實，在騰訊收購樂遊後表示：「在目前的狀況下，我們確定無法繼續以遊戲名稱繼續開發專案。」<br />\n <br />\n「我們很喜愛《魔戒》IP，也很遺憾我們無法將這款作品帶給玩家們。」"},{"pid":"85c1b76e6cfd6f96e93f9dc482c4bf58f4613af6","tid":2495204,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:03:21.000Z","msg":"騰訊可能想搶魔戒IP整手機game？定係將收費方式定為30級VVIP，大量課金P2W元素？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAmazon遊戲界良心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw當年玩LOTRO真係好震撼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如此龐大嘅MMO世界<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yPYC4hzoiQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyPYC4hzoiQQ&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=8ae998eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yPYC4hzoiQQ</a>"},{"pid":"c53bd81e70f6faba1de60e0b3ca2e1565c85ac21","tid":2495204,"uid":59328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:07:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ymUEPKTEQaQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FymUEPKTEQaQ&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqx3Kg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=22ec29ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ymUEPKTEQaQ</a><br />\n魔戒歧視獸人加劇現實種族歧視可恥 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94378ac757a62918b02c86f650bebb7b529789c","tid":2495204,"uid":41414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:25:06.000Z","msg":"可惜 咁睇黎原本會係好驚"},{"pid":"832f008c5a733d3a997dd92136ba164a98bae84b","tid":2495204,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:34:19.000Z","msg":"聽個名就知間樂遊係中国佬開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85a9a4e831ba2d213b724567bcd71bba7388c17a","tid":2495204,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"832f008c5a733d3a997dd92136ba164a98bae84b","tid":2495204,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:34:19.000Z","msg":"聽個名就知間樂遊係中国佬開 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:37:43.000Z","msg":"Leyou<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}